OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FDonald Trump has said US negotiators
OL,7,Fwill head to Pakistan on Monday for
OL,8,Fanother round of talks with Iran,
OL,9,Fraising hopes of extending a fragile
OL,10,Fceasefire set to expire on Wednesday,
OL,11,Feven as Washington and Tehran remain
OL,12,Fin a standoff over the Strait of
OL,13,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
