OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776615077
OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FIran did not immediately confirm the
OL,7,Ftalks, but its chief negotiator,
OL,8,Fparliament speaker Mohammed Bagher
OL,9,FQalibaf, said in an interview aired on
OL,10,Fstate television late on Saturday that
OL,11,F"there will be no retreat in the field
OL,12,Fof diplomacy," while acknowledging a
OL,13,Fwide gap remained between the sides.
OL,15,FThe White House said Vice President JD
OL,16,FVance, who led the first round of
OL,17,Fhistoric face-to-face talks last
OL,18,Fweekend, would lead the delegation to
OL,19,FPakistan with envoys Steve Witkoff and
OL,20,FJared Kushner.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@NO]
