OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776615077
OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FPakistani authorities have already
OL,7,Fbegun tightening security in
OL,8,FIslamabad, mirroring the similar near
OL,9,Fcitywide lockdown that was implemented
OL,10,Fduring the last round of talks.
OL,12,FIran on Saturday said it had received
OL,13,Fnew proposals from the United States.
OL,15,FIt was unclear whether either side had
OL,16,Fshifted stances on issues that
OL,17,Fderailed the last round of
OL,18,Fnegotiations, including Iran's nuclear
OL,19,Fenrichment program, its funding for
OL,20,Forganisations like Hezbollah and
OL,21,Fcontrol over the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
