OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FTrump's announcement repeated his
OL,7,Fthreats against Iranian infrastructure
OL,8,Fthat have drawn widespread criticism
OL,9,Fand warnings of war crimes.
OL,11,FIf Iran doesn't agree to the US-
OL,12,Fproposed deal, "the United States is
OL,13,Fgoing to knock out every single Power
OL,14,FPlant, and every single Bridge, in
OL,15,FIran," he wrote.
OL,17,FStrait of Hormuz remains closed after
OL,18,Fmixed messages from Iran
