OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FShips remained unable to transit the
OL,7,Fcritical waterway amid threats from
OL,8,FIran and a US blockade on ships
OL,9,Fheading to and from Iranian ports.
OL,11,FRoughly one-fifth of the world's oil
OL,12,Ftrade normally passes through the
OL,13,Fstrait, and the global energy crisis
OL,14,Fthreatened to deepen as the war is now
OL,15,Fin its eighth week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
