OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FIranian officials earlier on Sunday
OL,7,Fheld firm that ships wouldn't pass
OL,8,Fwhile the US blockade remained in
OL,9,Feffect. "It is impossible for others
OL,10,Fto pass through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,11,Fwhile we cannot," Qalibaf said.
OL,13,FIn his post about talks, Trump accused
OL,14,FIran of violating the ceasefire by
OL,15,Ffiring at ships transiting the strait.
OL,16,FIran has called the US blockade a
OL,17,Fviolation, and foreign ministry
OL,18,Fspokesperson Esmaeil Baqaei on Sunday
OL,19,Fcalled it an "act of aggression."
