OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FIran had announced the strait's
OL,7,Freopening after a 10-day truce between
OL,8,FIsrael and the Iranian-backed
OL,9,FHezbollah militant group in Lebanon
OL,10,Ftook hold on Friday.
OL,12,FBut Iran said it would continue
OL,13,Fenforcing its restrictions there after
OL,14,FTrump said the US blockade "will
OL,15,Fremain in full force" until Tehran
OL,16,Freaches a deal with the United States.
