OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FAfter a brief uptick in transit
OL,7,Fattempts on Saturday, Iran fired on
OL,8,Ftwo India-flagged merchant ships that
OL,9,Fwere forced to turn around, leading
OL,10,FIndia to summon Iran's ambassador over
OL,11,Fthe "serious incident."
OL,13,FIndia noted that Iran earlier let
OL,14,Fseveral India-bound ships through.
OL,16,FPakistan continues to lead diplomatic
OL,17,Fefforts
