OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FPakistani Foreign Minister Ishaq Dar,
OL,7,Fwho spoke by phone with Iran's Foreign
OL,8,FMinister Abbas Araghchi on Sunday, has
OL,9,Fsaid his country was working to
OL,10,F"bridge" differences between the US
OL,11,Fand Iran.
OL,13,FIranian Deputy Foreign Minister Saeed
OL,14,FKhatibzadeh on Saturday said that the
OL,15,FUS is "risking the whole ceasefire
OL,16,Fpackage" with its blockade.
OL,18,FKhatibzadeh said Iran won't hand over
OL,19,Fits stock of 440kg of enriched uranium
OL,20,Fto the United States, calling the idea
OL,21,F"a nonstarter."
