OL,3,CDonald Trump says negotiations with
OL,4,CIran to resume in Pakistan on Monday
OL,6,FThe deputy minister didn't address
OL,7,Fother proposals for the enriched
OL,8,Furanium, saying only that "we are
OL,9,Fready to address any concerns.
OL,11,FThe war has killed at least 3,000
OL,12,Fpeople in Iran, more than 2,290 in
OL,13,FLebanon, 23 in Israel and more than a
OL,14,Fdozen in Gulf Arab states. Fifteen
OL,15,FIsraeli soldiers in Lebanon and 13 US
OL,16,Fservice members throughout the region
OL,17,Fhave been killed.
